column3: Does the new Battlestar Galactica series have more episodes than the old one?
column5:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
ASK 
WHERE {
	<http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battlestar_Galactica_%281978_TV_series%29> dbo:numberOfEpisodes ?x .
	<http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battlestar_Galactica_%282004_TV_series%29> dbo:numberOfEpisodes ?y .
	FILTER (?y > ?x)
}

column3: Who is the youngest Darts player?
column4: "Who is the youngest DartsPlayer?"
column5:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri
WHERE {
        ?uri rdf:type dbo:DartsPlayer .
        ?uri dbo:birthDate ?date .
}
ORDER BY DESC(?date)
OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

column3: Who was the pope that founded the Vatican Television?
column4: "Who was the pope that founded Vatican Television Center?"
column5:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> 
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> 
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> 
SELECT ?uri 
WHERE { 
         ?uri rdf:type dbo:Pope . 
         res:Vatican_Television_Center dbo:foundedBy ?uri .
}

column3: Who is starring in Spanish movies produced by Benicio del Toro?
column5: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?film <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Film> . ?film <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/country> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain> . ?film <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/producer> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benicio_del_Toro> . ?film <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/starring> ?uri . ?uri <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Person> . }
